{"tid":1642510,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［共識］五大訴求 缺一不可 Five demands, Not one less","createTime":"2019-10-09T17:41:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T15:40:49.000Z","uid":65210,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"904341918a3351c58dfb8770722de9ffd821bf68","tid":1642510,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:41:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><ins>五大訴求 缺一不可</ins></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><em>五大訴求：</em></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<em>1:撤回惡法：適用於送中條例、緊急法 &mdash; 蒙面法 、將來有機會由緊急法所立的任何惡法<br />\n2:收回暴動定性<br />\n3:釋放被捕人士並撤銷控罪<br />\n4:成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n5:立即實行雙普選</em><strong><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n</strong><br />\n隔離Post見到有<em>六大訴求</em> 定 <em>五大訴求</em> 嘅爭議<br />\n就如已經撤回逃犯條例後<br />\n大家叫口號仍然係：「<ins><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>五大訴求 缺一不可</strong></span></ins>！」<br />\n缺一不可 係一樣野都不能少 亦不宜加減<br />\n明白大家對於局勢變化以及黑警濫權嘅嚴重性 <br />\n會想增加解放警隊等訴求<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n問題係<br />\n由始至終 呢一場反送中運動都係講緊「五大訴求 缺一不可」<br />\n一轉變做六大訴求<br />\n就會令到外國政客 外媒 中立/淺黃嘅香港市民<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>感到混淆</strong></span><br />\n亦會顯得抗爭者對五大訴求不堅定<br />\n更加有機會令到某啲人提出「七大訴求、八大訴求」<br />\n造成示威人士得一想二嘅形象 <br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong>所以改口號做六大訴求<br />\n只會帶來混亂及負面影響</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n請堅持五大訴求 <br />\n無論有幾多種「實質」訴求 <br />\n只要係Base on五大訴求大方向就無問題<br />\n真係實行嘅時候再斟酌都未遲<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但口號上<br />\n一定要繼續叫「五大訴求 缺一不可」<br />\n直至抗爭成功為止<br />\n<br />\n</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"aefe7bdffad8bfdd75f98251df2a10f743b790ec","tid":1642510,"uid":173058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:58:14.000Z","msg":"推，訴求呢樣嘢真係唔可以亂改<br />\n而且爭取到真普選，之後想做咩都有得諗<br />\n冇真普選咩都唔洗諗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">真雙普選 唯一出路</span></span>"},{"pid":"c5ee10542f9ef8f6c86b74f60448893a11fc8f5a","tid":1642510,"uid":62746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:00:22.000Z","msg":"agree"},{"pid":"72dfff20fc2674fb953ec667d492b93771e1bdd0","tid":1642510,"uid":185426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:01:22.000Z","msg":"五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"88524572573a06c9e795dbac93644e40e12edb75","tid":1642510,"uid":158426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:06:29.000Z","msg":"exact7ly<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span>"},{"pid":"e8c36aaad9ef146db117ad1c73b445baf00d8759","tid":1642510,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88524572573a06c9e795dbac93644e40e12edb75","tid":1642510,"uid":158426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:06:29.000Z","msg":"exact7ly<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:17:45.000Z","msg":"多謝同意 <br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"f9f9f4530bd07ca2d3f9e154974d2d5c6ac1a445","tid":1642510,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aefe7bdffad8bfdd75f98251df2a10f743b790ec","tid":1642510,"uid":173058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T17:58:14.000Z","msg":"推，訴求呢樣嘢真係唔可以亂改<br />\n而且爭取到真普選，之後想做咩都有得諗<br />\n冇真普選咩都唔洗諗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">真雙普選 唯一出路</span></span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T18:18:29.000Z","msg":"有啲野擺心入面 大家都明<br />\n唔駛講出面<br />\n但訴求一定要繼續講五大訴求"},{"pid":"fe8561138ded5e13be1bbdd96a321249d6672f29","tid":1642510,"uid":173058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f9f9f4530bd07ca2d3f9e154974d2d5c6ac1a445","tid":1642510,"uid":65210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aefe7bdffad8bfdd75f98251df2a10f743b790ec","tid":1642510